6/ Question the narrative. Dig deeper. Make up your own mind and always objectively look at both sides of any story - no mater if its politics, geopolitics or even a piece of artwork. The truth hides always somewhere in the middle.

5/ I am a pacifist and against this war. However I am also intelligent enough to understand and see the big picture of where this is heading. I feel sorry for those brainwashed people that don't understand whats really going on.
4/ I am aware that freedom of the press died a long time ago, both in the East and the West. But at least you had the opportunity to hear both sides, make up your own mind, back in time.

3/ fake news and propaganda. It is not a one way street.  If you hear only ONE side of the story it is very likely that you will be sooner or later fed propaganda and fake news, thats unavoidable. And you sheeple walk right into the trap.
